    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit maintains exceptional compression across all cylinders and retains its signature 8,000 RPM redline performance. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory-calibrated variable M differential lock for superior power distribution. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and proactive subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity. The suspension geometry remains true, benefiting from recent bushing replacements and a precise alignment. While the finish exhibits minor aesthetic patina expected of a driven enthusiast vehicle, the powertrain and drivetrain synchronization are dialed-in for immediate track or spirited canyon use.",
