      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-loved, super dependable, and it still runs like a dream! It\u2019s the perfect fit if you're looking for a quality car that\u2019s ready for the road without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019d love to see it go to a great new home. Feel free to give me a shout if you have any questions!",
